title: 'rustc' panicked at 'found unstable fingerprints for extern_mod_stmt_cnum(<project>[d5a7]::rocket)'

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
The bug was not reproducible to me as it disappeared after a `cargo clean`. So i think it has a low priority. ### Meta `rustc --version --verbose`: ``` rustc 1.52.0-nightly (acca81892 2021-03-13) binary: rustc commit-hash: acca818928654807ed3bc1ce0e97df118f8716c8 commit-date: 2021-03-13 host: x86_64-apple-darwin release: 1.52.0-nightly LLVM version: 12.0.0 ``` ### Error output ``` thread 'rustc' panicked at 'found unstable fingerprints for extern_mod_stmt_cnum(doorcam[d5a7]::rocket)', /rustc/acca818928654807ed3bc1ce0e97df118f8716c8/compiler/rustc_query_system/src/query/plumbing.rs:593:5 note: run with `RUST_BACKTRACE=1` environment variable to display a backtrace error: internal compiler error: unexpected panic note: the compiler unexpectedly panicked. this is a bug. note: we would appreciate a bug report: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/new?labels=C-bug%2C+I-ICE%2C+T-compiler&template=ice.md note: rustc 1.52.0-nightly (acca81892 2021-03-13) running on x86_64-apple-darwin note: compiler flags: -C embed-bitcode=no -C debuginfo=2 -C incremental --crate-type bin note: some of the compiler flags provided by cargo are hidden query stack during panic: #0 [extern_mod_stmt_cnum] computing crate imported by `rocket` #1 [check_mod_unstable_api_usage] checking for unstable API usage in top-level module end of query stack error: could not compile `doorcam` ```
Backtrace

``` stack backtrace: 0: _rust_begin_unwind 1: std::panicking::begin_panic_fmt 2: rustc_query_system::query::plumbing::incremental_verify_ich 3: rustc_query_system::query::plumbing::load_from_disk_and_cache_in_memory 4: rustc_data_structures::stack::ensure_sufficient_stack 5: rustc_query_system::query::plumbing::get_query_impl 6: ::extern_mod_stmt_cnum 7: ::visit_item 8: rustc_middle::hir::map::Map::visit_item_likes_in_module 9: rustc_passes::stability::check_mod_unstable_api_usage 10: rustc_middle::dep_graph::::with_deps 11: rustc_query_system::dep_graph::graph::DepGraph::with_task_impl 12: rustc_data_structures::stack::ensure_sufficient_stack 13: rustc_query_system::query::plumbing::force_query_with_job 14: rustc_query_system::query::plumbing::get_query_impl 15: ::check_mod_unstable_api_usage 16: std::panic::catch_unwind 17: rustc_session::utils::::time 18: rustc_interface::passes::analysis 19: rustc_middle::dep_graph::::with_deps 20: rustc_query_system::dep_graph::graph::DepGraph::with_task_impl 21: rustc_data_structures::stack::ensure_sufficient_stack 22: rustc_query_system::query::plumbing::force_query_with_job 23: rustc_query_system::query::plumbing::get_query_impl 24: ::analysis 25: rustc_interface::passes::QueryContext::enter 26: rustc_interface::queries::::enter 27: rustc_span::with_source_map 28: scoped_tls::ScopedKey::set ```
